=You're provided a scrape of a LinkedIn company page. Your task is to extract the "About Us" section and any posts or content from the last 2 weeks.

Return in this JSON format:

{"companyLinkedin":"about goes here"}
{"recentPost":"Posts and content goes here"}

Rules:
- If either is companyLinkedin or recentPost has no data, then output "no content"
- Include date with and posts or content

